text: Speaking of Two Hearted, if anyone knows where to get it please let me know. I’ve been aching for it ever since I left Michigan. Definitely one of my favorite beers.

You're in luck <@U5ZLKG7FW>, I have been seeing Two Hearted around town on taps recently, it's trending... I don't know where it might be on tap right this minute, but Belmont Station is likely to have it in bottles
Oooo…I’ve been hearing about Belmont Station. I’ll have to check it out. I miss my Bell’s and Founder’s mainstays. Maybe I’ll see a Dirty Bastard pop up sometime. That’d be a treat.
I checked my untappd history and I first had it at the Rogue pub just down the street... and my friends have seen it at Bailey's from time to time
<@U5ZLKG7FW> my go-to is Beaumont Market on 42nd and Fremont. I was upstate NY last weekend and saw Two Hearted at a gas station and shed a small tear for our relative lack.
